  <header>
    
      <h1 class="entry-title"><a href="/blog/2014/01/20/michael-buble-feeling-good/">Michael Buble - Feeling Good</a></h1>
    
    
      <p class="meta">
        








  


<time datetime="2014-01-20T11:56:00-08:00" pubdate data-updated="true">Jan 20<span>th</span>, 2014</time>
        

<span class="categories">
  published in 
  
    <a class='category' href='/blog/topics/song/'>Song</a>
  
</span>


        
          <a href="/blog/2014/01/20/michael-buble-feeling-good/#disqus_thread">Comments</a>
        
      </p>
    
  </header>


  <div class="entry-content"><div class="video-container">
  <iframe width="640" height="480" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/Edwsf-8F3sI" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
</div>


<p>I don&rsquo;t even care that Michael Bublé&rsquo;s fanbase is mostly middle-aged women. I&rsquo;m not ashamed to admit that I love this song, and Michael Bublé&rsquo;s version is incredible. Were I not so confident in my manhood, I might have posted <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CmwRQqJsegw">Muse&rsquo;s version</a> instead. Listen to whichever one floats your boat.</p>
</div>
  
  


    </article>
  
  
