      <p class="meta">
        








  


<time datetime="2014-01-20T01:29:00-08:00" pubdate data-updated="true">Jan 20<span>th</span>, 2014</time>
        

<span class="categories">
  published in 
  
    <a class='category' href='/blog/topics/song/'>Song</a>
  
</span>


        
          <a href="/blog/2014/01/20/imogen-heap-hide-and-seek/#disqus_thread">Comments</a>
        
      </p>
    
  </header>


  <div class="entry-content"><div class="video-container">
  <iframe width="640" height="480" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/UYIAfiVGluk" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
</div>


<p>I used to love falling asleep to this song when I was younger. Such a beautiful, creative, and simple arrangement, and the lyrics are pure poetry.</p>
